we love GOODREVIEW monty s our son has egg and dariy allergies and we love GOODREVIEW all the vegan options they have breakfast is the trickiest meal for our son because almost all breakfast foods contain eggs and dairy but there are several options for our entire family our son s favorite is the tofu scramble with their potatoes come early on a saturday or sunday the wait can get long but worth it one of my favorite things is the blue plate special omelette with bacon avocado cheese and salsa on top i also really enjoy the vegan hash and in not even vegan i also like to come for lunch their meatloaf is delicious and the vegan sandwich with portobello mushrooms avacados and lemon tahini dressing i m just sad monty s isn t closer to our house
